#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:2
msgid "元件配置"
msgstr "Component Configuration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:4
msgid "在模板编辑器的元件视图中，选中目标元件后，可在右侧\"模板\"栏查看并编辑其全部属性参数。"
msgstr ""
"In the Template Editor's Component view, selecting a component exposes every"
" property in the **Template** panel on the right, ready to review and edit."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:-1
msgid "参数设置示例"
msgstr "Parameter-editor example"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:11
msgid "元件基本信息"
msgstr "Basic component info"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:13
msgid "**丝印/位号/标识**：必填，建议与 PCB 丝印一致，便于检测时快速定位。"
msgstr ""
"**Designator**: required. Use the value printed on the PCB silkscreen so the"
" component is easy to locate at inspection time."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:14
msgid "**料号**：可选，填写该元件的物料编码，便于后续按料号分组与统计。"
msgstr ""
"**Part Number**: optional. Filling it in enables later grouping and "
"statistics by PN."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:15
msgid "**封装号**：填写该元件的封装名称，便于后续按封装分组与统计。"
msgstr ""
"**Package**: the component's package name; enables later grouping and "
"statistics by package."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:18
msgid "对齐参数"
msgstr "Alignment parameters"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:20
msgid ""
"**需要在检测中对齐**：是否启用该元件的对齐功能，默认开启。启用后，系统会在检测时自动调整该元件的位置与旋转角度，确保其与模板位置一致。被设为坏板标记时，该开关强制关闭并禁用。"
msgstr ""
"**Require alignment during inspection**: whether to align this component at "
"inspection time. On by default. When enabled, the system auto-adjusts the "
"component's position and rotation to match the template. The switch is "
"locked off and disabled when the component is configured as a badmark."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:21
msgid ""
"**启用AI对齐**：为该元件启用基于 AI 的对齐，进一步减小残余位移，适用于对位敏感的元件（如细间距 BGA、小字符 "
"OCR）。与\"需要在检测中对齐\"互为补充，可独立启用。"
msgstr ""
"**Enable AI Alignment**: enables AI-based alignment to further reduce "
"residual shift; useful for alignment-sensitive components (fine-pitch BGAs, "
"small-character OCR). Complementary to **Require alignment during "
"inspection** — toggle the two independently."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:22
msgid ""
"**必须在视野中心捕获**：启用后，路径规划器将为该元件专门生成一个以其为中心的视野停靠点，确保该元件始终位于相机视野中心进行拍摄，以提升光学质量，适用于尺寸微小的"
" OCR 或细间距 BGA 元件。对齐与此开关正交互补。修改后需通过\"重载检测\"使设置生效。"
msgstr ""
"**Must Capture at FOV Center**: when enabled, the path planner emits a "
"dedicated camera stop centered on this component, so it is always imaged in "
"the middle of the field of view. Improves optical quality for tiny OCR and "
"fine-pitch BGAs. Orthogonal to the alignment switches above. Changes take "
"effect only after **Reload Inference**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:23
msgid ""
"**检测允许偏移 (mm)**：当整个 PCB "
"板的偏移超过设定值时，将不会对齐该元件，避免误对齐导致检测失败。仅在\"需要在检测中对齐\"开启时可编辑。"
msgstr ""
"**Allowed shift (mm)**: when the whole PCB's shift exceeds this value, the "
"component is not aligned — avoiding bad alignments that would break "
"inspection. Editable only when **Require alignment during inspection** is "
"on."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:24
msgid "**检测允许旋转 (°)**：当整个 PCB 板的旋转超过设定值时，将不会对齐该元件。仅在\"需要在检测中对齐\"开启时可编辑。"
msgstr ""
"**Allowed rotation (°)**: when the whole PCB's rotation exceeds this value, "
"the component is not aligned. Editable only when **Require alignment during "
"inspection** is on."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:29
msgid "坏板标记"
msgstr "Badmark"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:31
msgid "**坏板标记**：将元件用作\"坏板标记\"，用于驱动子板（拼板联）的良率判定。可选三种模式："
msgstr ""
"**Badmark**: configure the component as a *badmark* used to drive the sub-"
"board yield decision in a panel. Three options:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:33
msgid "**非坏板标记**：普通检测元件（默认）。"
msgstr "**Not a badmark**: an ordinary inspection component (default)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:34
msgid "**坏板标记 — 通过表示好板**：该标记检测通过 ⇒ 所在子板视为好板。"
msgstr ""
"**Badmark — pass means good**: when this badmark passes inspection, its sub-"
"board is treated as a good board."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:35
msgid "**坏板标记 — 通过表示坏板**：该标记检测通过 ⇒ 所在子板视为坏板。"
msgstr ""
"**Badmark — pass means bad**: when this badmark passes inspection, its sub-"
"board is treated as a bad board."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:37
msgid "约束与联动："
msgstr "Constraints and side-effects:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:39
msgid ""
"坏板标记必须位于子板位置（拼板的子板内，不可在拼板共享区域）；如尚未注册基板，请先注册。当元件不在子板位置（``array_index`` 为 "
"``-1`` 或未设置）时，选择框禁用。"
msgstr ""
"A badmark must live inside a sub-board (within a panel's sub-board, not in "
"the shared-panel area). Register the base panel first if you haven't. The "
"selector is disabled when the component isn't on a sub-board "
"(``array_index`` is ``-1`` or unset)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:40
msgid ""
"设为坏板标记后，**需要在检测中对齐**、**基准产品中是否NG** 两个开关将被强制关闭并禁用；**同步ROI** "
"须保持开启（保存时由服务端校验，否则返回 400 错误）。"
msgstr ""
"Once configured as a badmark, both **Require alignment during inspection** "
"and **NG on the golden product** are locked off and disabled; **Sync ROI** "
"must stay on (the server validates this at save time and returns 400 "
"otherwise)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:41
msgid "坏板标记驱动子板判定，但**不计入**复检 NG 列表与数据分析报告（报表中的总数/报警数/NG 数均排除坏板标记）。"
msgstr ""
"Badmarks drive the sub-board verdict but are **not counted** in the review "
"NG list or the data-analysis report — Total / Alerted / NG counts all "
"exclude badmarks."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:44
msgid "检测跳过"
msgstr "Skip inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:46
msgid "**跳过此元件的检测**：将该元件实例排除在检测之外，不进行推理、不产生检测结果、不计入良率。被设为坏板标记时，该开关强制关闭并禁用。"
msgstr ""
"**Skip inspection on this component**: excludes this component instance from"
" inspection entirely — no inference, no result, not counted in yield. The "
"switch is locked off and disabled when the component is a badmark."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:47
msgid "**跳过检测 (料号)**：按料号将该元件整体排除在检测之外。当元件有料号时显示。跳过操作会传播至所有相同料号的实例。"
msgstr ""
"**Skip inspection (by Part No.)**: exclude the component from inspection by "
"part number. Shown when the PN is set. Propagates to every instance sharing "
"the same PN."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:48
msgid "**跳过检测 (封装号)**：按封装号将该元件整体排除在检测之外。当元件有封装号时显示。"
msgstr ""
"**Skip inspection (by Package No.)**: exclude the component from inspection "
"by package number. Shown when the package is set."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:51
msgid "其他开关"
msgstr "Other switches"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:53
msgid ""
"**基准产品中是否NG**：用于拼板子板实例（``array_index > "
"0``），标记该位置在基准良品板上本身即为异常（如缺件），从而在检测时不将其误报为缺陷。被设为坏板标记时，该开关强制关闭并禁用。"
msgstr ""
"**NG on the golden product**: used on sub-board instances (``array_index > "
"0``). Marks the location as already-NG on the golden board (e.g. missing on "
"purpose) so inspection doesn't falsely flag it. Locked off and disabled when"
" the component is a badmark."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:54
msgid ""
"**同步ROI**：控制该元件在子板中的 ROI（检测区域）是否与主板保持一致。关闭后，可在每个子板单独调整该元件的 ROI，适用于拼版中局部差异场景。"
msgstr ""
"**Sync ROI**: whether the component's ROI on the sub-board stays in sync "
"with the base sub-board. Turn it off to tune the ROI on each sub-board "
"independently — useful when local panel variations exist."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:55
msgid "**连接封装**：关联该元件至对应封装分组，实现训练样本聚合与参数统一管理。关闭后，该元件可独立设置参数，不参与封装组同步。"
msgstr ""
"**Link Package**: ties this component to its package group so training "
"samples aggregate and parameters stay in sync. Turn it off to tune this "
"component independently from the package group."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:56
msgid "**连接料号**：关联该元件至对应料号分组，便于同料号元件批量训练与参数同步。关闭后，该元件不参与料号组的参数继承。"
msgstr ""
"**Link Part No.**: ties this component to its part-number group for batch "
"training and parameter sync. Turn it off to opt out of part-number-level "
"inheritance."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:59
msgid "操作按钮"
msgstr "Action buttons"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:61
msgid "**保存**：保存当前元件的属性与参数设置。有未保存更改时按钮高亮显示。"
msgstr ""
"**Save**: persist the current property and parameter changes. The button is "
"highlighted when there are unsaved changes."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:62
msgid "**绘制ROI**：在当前元件上绘制新的 ROI 区域（仅支持主板实例 ``array_index = 0``）。"
msgstr ""
"**Draw ROI**: draw a new ROI on this component (supported only on the base "
"sub-board instance, ``array_index = 0``)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:63
msgid "**用库中的模板替换**：从私有元件库中选择一个已保存的标准化元件，替换当前选中的元件，便于复用已有模板。"
msgstr ""
"**Replace with template from library**: pick a saved standardized component "
"from the private library and replace the current selection — convenient for "
"reusing existing templates."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:64
msgid "**在组中添加ROI**：在已分组的元件基础上，为该元件添加新的 ROI（检测区域）。"
msgstr ""
"**Add ROI to group**: add a new ROI to a component that is already grouped."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:68
msgid ""
"替代料（Variation）面板在元件为替代料时显示，用于管理替代料的料号/封装号重命名及批量复制操作。详见 "
":doc:`../features/variations` 页面，此处不重复说明。"
msgstr ""
"The **Variation** panel is shown only when the component is a variation; it "
"manages the variation's part-number / package-number renames and bulk-copy "
"operations. See :doc:`../features/variations` for the details — not repeated"
" here."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:71
msgid "**常见问题与提示**"
msgstr "**Common questions and tips**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:75
msgid "**元件对齐 / 定位问题：**"
msgstr "**Alignment / localization issues:**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:77
msgid "**小料元件定位不准 / 误报多**：先确保第一块拼板的本体框对齐，再点击 **自动对齐元件**，其他拼板会自动跟随对齐。"
msgstr ""
"**Small parts are localized poorly / produce many false positives**: first "
"make sure the body box on the first sub-board is aligned, then click **Auto-"
"align Components**; the other sub-boards follow automatically."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:78
msgid "**大料居中后偏斜**：可关闭该元件的 **AI 对齐**；将 **允许偏移距离** 调小一些，避免较大偏移时定位过头。"
msgstr ""
"**Large parts skew after being centered**: turn off **AI Alignment** on the "
"component and reduce **Allowed shift** so a large shift can't overshoot."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/component_settings.rst:79
msgid "**整体元件偏移、焊锡检测误报**：确认产品已启用 **拼板对齐** 与 **元件对齐**；同样可将允许偏移距离调小。"
msgstr ""
"**Overall component shift causes solder false positives**: confirm that both"
" **Panel Alignment** and **Component Alignment** are enabled on the product,"
" and consider reducing the allowed shift."

